{"tid":550998,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"入「城」不成玩失蹤，馬列斯聽罰220萬","createTime":"2018-02-05T09:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T09:25:00.000Z","uid":60286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0725ed5094fc7f26de4e58d791245f372e6839","tid":550998,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"英超李斯特城主力馬列斯在轉會窗關閉前，向李城遞交轉會呈請，並自行決定不隨隊在週三作客愛華頓，惟交易最後亦未能成事。這位阿爾及利亞國腳疑因不滿轉會失敗，繼續罷工向李城抗議，連續5日缺操，至今仍然無法聯繫，看來覆水難收，關係破裂。雖未有官方聲明證實一切，但報導指球會將會向此子開出20萬鎊的罰單。<br />\n <br />\n此前報導指曼城曾提出以球員加現金交換馬列斯，合共價更高達6,500萬鎊，但遠低於李城要求的9,500萬鎊估價。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/171449_b30c10c70ff94c2c1a0324ee2cdc5b2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F171449_b30c10c70ff94c2c1a0324ee2cdc5b2c.jpg&h=5d2d7a39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51b4d652b6106d2bbd952b9025c829bdf360fa72","tid":550998,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:17:37.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本一早要反面"},{"pid":"148c2a338e959a86eb9d19220a3fb3a4e4ad2d8f","tid":550998,"uid":73340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:25:00.000Z","msg":"變自由身啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}